flowchart TD
    A[Bash command intercepted] --> B[Hook 1: regex_filter.py]
    B --> C{Rule 1: block_sensitive_data<br/>API keys, tokens, passwords?}
    C -->|Match| D[DENY - credentials detected]
    C -->|No match| E{Rule 2: allow_trusted_endpoints<br/>localhost, GitHub, PyPI, etc.?}
    E -->|Match| F[ALLOW - trusted host]
    E -->|No match| G{Rule 3: block_untrusted_network<br/>curl, wget, requests, ssh, etc.?}
    G -->|Match| H[DENY - untrusted network call]
    G -->|No match| I[ALLOW - no regex rules triggered]

    I --> J[Hook 2: llm_filter.py]
    F --> J
    J --> K{NLP plugin available?}
    K -->|No| L[ALLOW - no plugin, skip NLP]
    K -->|Yes| M{PII detected?<br/>email, SSN, credit card, name...}
    M -->|Yes, above threshold| N[DENY - PII found]
    M -->|No| O[ALLOW - clean]

    style D fill:#ff6b6b,color:#fff
    style H fill:#ff6b6b,color:#fff
    style N fill:#ff6b6b,color:#fff
    style F fill:#51cf66,color:#fff
    style I fill:#51cf66,color:#fff
    style L fill:#51cf66,color:#fff
    style O fill:#51cf66,color:#fff
